But to purſue the Thread of my diſcourſe; 
Arg. p. 13. 
after this ſmall Digreſſion, I am of Opinion, that more Millions of Sacrifices have been offered up, of the Noblest Humane Blood and Treaſure, to thoſe two Impudent Monsters, Quacks in Phyſick, and Empericks in Law, than either of the three Monsters above mentioned. And now I will give an inſtance of the Latter.
